    "captions": [
      {
        "text": "A cave explorer vanished beneath Kentucky soil in nineteen twenty five.",
        "position": {
          "start": 0.0,
          "end": 4.4
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Floyd Collins chased fame, squeezing through impossibly narrow limestone tunnels.",
        "position": {
          "start": 4.0,
          "end": 8.0
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "A falling rock pinned his ankle, sealing him in total darkness.",
        "position": {
          "start": 8.8,
          "end": 13.2
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "He survived on raw eggs and sips of muddy groundwater.",
        "position": {
          "start": 12.32,
          "end": 17.48
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Hundreds of volunteers dug frantically, passing buckets through collapsing dirt.",
        "position": {
          "start": 18.22,
          "end": 22.6
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Reporters broadcast every update, turning tragedy into a national spectacle.",
        "position": {
          "start": 23.36,
          "end": 27.76
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "After eighteen grueling days, rescuers finally broke through his final wall.",
        "position": {
          "start": 27.76,
          "end": 32.76
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "They found him motionless, his flashlight long since burned out.",
        "position": {
          "start": 33.42,
          "end": 36.84
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "His story reshaped cave rescue protocols and birthed modern national parks.",
        "position": {
          "start": 37.36,
          "end": 41.76
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000",
          "stroke_width": 3
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Some legends aren\u2019t born from triumph, but from quiet endurance.",
        "position": {
          "start": 42.46,
          "end": 45.82
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
